WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:22.000
This walkthrough uses a deterministic synthetic workspace. No social provider is contacted.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:49.000
The dashboard summarizes account readiness and recent activity, with composition as the primary action.

00:00:49.000 --> 00:01:20.000
Provider accounts expose capabilities and are visibly marked simulated; OAuth is disabled in demo mode.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:58.000
The composer validates content, optional links, media support, and the exact selected targets.

00:01:58.000 --> 00:02:17.000
Each provider target enters publishing without an optimistic success claim.

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:49.000
Deterministic results complete with synthetic external identifiers; no provider endpoint was called.

00:02:49.000 --> 00:03:10.000
Historical retry evidence preserves attempts and terminal status per target.

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:46.000
Analytics reports application counts and follower snapshot deltas, not individual unfollower claims.

00:03:46.000 --> 00:04:05.000
Tests, builds, audits, secret scanning, responsive checks, and browser automation support the local MVP claim.

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:22.000
Provider approval, live OAuth, deployment, retention, and operations remain explicit external gates.
